{"tid":1592502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[加拿大撚] 旗幟鮮明地為929抗共聯盟集氣","createTime":"2019-09-24T15:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T21:33:12.000Z","uid":310649,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"58599cff2b10fb22828a95ac4ee34b5d87f8b39b","tid":1592502,"uid":310649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:46:37.000Z","msg":"岩岩星期日922，當身在香港嘅你地為未來奮鬥嘅同時，係卡加里Calgary呢個加拿大中部埠仔，長年被中共壓迫嘅民族終於團結起來，向暴政説不！向香港嘅你地打氣！向不公義宣戰！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fZgB2a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfZgB2a0.jpg&h=62499026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事緣海外共賊通常會係十一國殤前一兩星期大肆「慶祝」，自己圍爐打飛機之餘，仲想向外國輸出「太平盛世 經濟起飛」嘅假象。趁著佢地黨慶，香港人聯同西藏人，東突厥維吾爾人（被稱新彊），台灣人及越南人一行二百人，一眾被法西斯中共打壓、殘害嘅民族，向世界揭示佢地嘅真面目，反抗極權！<br />\n<br />\n當日精華：<br />\n1. <a href=\"https://streamable.com/3aauu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F3aauu&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=2e192104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/3aauu</a><br />\n2. <a href=\"https://streamable.com/sfso7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fsfso7&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=136533c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/sfso7</a><br />\n上埋local news (0:00-2:55)：<a href=\"https://calgary.ctvnews.ca/video?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcalgary.ctvnews.ca%2Fvideo%3F&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=1add8769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://calgary.ctvnews.ca/video?</a><br />\nclipId=1777778&amp;binId=1.2099013&amp;playlistPageNum=1<br />\n<br />\n929全球抗暴，將會係全球被迫害者站起來嘅時刻，We connect! 全球連成一線，向暴政說不，向不公義宣戰！屆時加拿大及世界各地城市將有不同形式集會，密切留意各地相關消息/fb專頁。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n驅逐共黨，打倒暴政！<br />\n<br />\n加拿大tg公海：<a href=\"http://t.me/unitedhkcanadian\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Funitedhkcanadian&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=c6c6e603\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/unitedhkcanadian</a><br />\n<br />\nFb: <br />\n加港同行 #cansavehk<br />\nFriends of Hong Kong Calgary <br />\nFriends of Hong Kong Edmonton<br />\nUCalgary Hong Kong Concern <br />\n<br />\n#HKinCrisis #StandwithHK"},{"pid":"eac7f0d2ec862399e5d5602ad5acbb47c51c655b","tid":1592502,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"c87f3b98b75dbc7406cb47b9f5729cb4a61834d1","tid":1592502,"uid":162663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:48:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8273ef53d72358360f59eaa80ebd08fabb37cf54","tid":1592502,"uid":162663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3ee3764e3303a016602859701d9b6202c4f8996","tid":1592502,"uid":162663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:48:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e772301190883066c1ed3fc9bce24cb190e9733","tid":1592502,"uid":162663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"香港人咁早瞓?"},{"pid":"a0195bf4d2172853b70316eb412f2c683fc35367","tid":1592502,"uid":185387,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">逐步整合post！推到有文宣！事關P牌開唔到自己post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">927</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-siz